# --- Analytics Configuration ---

# 1. LIVE CONVERSION & LEAD TRACKING (REAL DATA)
# This is already fully functional using your Supabase connection.
# No extra env vars are needed for this part.

# 2. VERCEL ANALYTICS (COLLECTION ONLY)
# Vercel collects data automatically when deployed. 
# Vercel currently does NOT provide a public API for fetching these stats into custom dashboards.
# To see these metrics, use your Vercel Project Dashboard.

# 3. TRAFFIC ANALYTICS (FOR PROGRAMMATIC ACCESS IN DASHBOARD)
# If you want traffic (Visitors, Pageviews) to show up in your custom dashboard,
# use Google Analytics 4 (GA4). You can set your GA4 ID in the SEO Settings page.
# To pull that data here, add:
# GA_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_EMAIL=your-service-account@project.iam.gserviceaccount.com
# GA_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_KEY="-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\n...\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----\n"
# GA_PROPERTY_ID=123456789

# 4. UNOFFICIAL VERCEL ACCESS (ADVANCED / NOT RECOMMENDED)
# If Vercel releases a programmatic API or for use with unofficial fetchers:
# VERCEL_TOKEN=your_personal_access_token
# VERCEL_PROJECT_ID=your_project_id
# VERCEL_TEAM_ID=your_team_id (if applicable)
